<m:mo> - </m:mo> 
<m:mi> ω </m:mi>
<m:mo mathvariant="bold"> k </m:mo>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-50">
The position vector of the particle at the given instant is :
</para>
<para id="element-51">
<m:math display="block">
